<deviceset name="WE-TDCHV_8038" prefix="L">
<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-TDC HV SMT Coupled Inductor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt; Characteristics&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;Low profile coupled inductor with 2.0kV Isolation
&lt;br&gt;Low losses and low Leakage Inductance
&lt;br&gt;Magnetical shielded
&lt;br&gt;1:1 Transformer
&lt;br&gt;Operation temperature: -40°C to +125°C
&lt;br&gt;Functional Isolation for a working voltage or 250VRMS
&lt;br&gt;Reference Designs
&lt;br&gt;RD006 3 W Dual-output isolated auxiliary supply for communication interfaces and measurement systems
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Applications&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;High density Isolated converter application (e.g. Flyback converter)
&lt;br&gt;Buck, Boost, Sepic, Zeta, CUK Converter
&lt;br&gt;Switching regulator with second unregulated output voltage
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/components/media/o14862v209%20Family_WE-TDC.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.we-online.com/components/media/o14862v209%20Family_WE-TDC.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="www.we-online.com/catalog/WE-TDCHV/?utm_source=eagle_model&amp;utm_medium=description_link&amp;utm_campaign=eisos_eagle"&gt;www.we-online.com/en/components/products/WE-TDCHV&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/b&gt;Updated by Ella 2026-05-13&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;2026 (C) Würth Elektronik</description>
